# FitDocs — Thư viện tài liệu Fitness
# Cursor Rules

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 16 (App Router) + TypeScript
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4 (dark mode default, zinc palette)
- Database: PostgreSQL via Drizzle ORM (src/lib/db.ts)
- Storage: AWS S3 (src/lib/s3.ts) — presigned URLs only, never expose raw S3 paths
- State: Zustand
- Validation: Zod
- Notifications: Sonner
- Date: date-fns

## Folder Structure
src/
  app/
    (user)/           # User-facing pages
    admin/            # Admin pages (password protected)
    api/              # API routes
  components/
    ui/               # Reusable UI primitives
    viewers/          # PDF, DOCX, Video viewers
    admin/            # Admin-specific components
  lib/
    db.ts             # Drizzle ORM client
    s3.ts             # S3 helper (presigned URLs)
    auth.ts           # Admin cookie auth (HMAC)
  db/
    schema.ts         # Drizzle schema definitions
    migrations/       # SQL migration files

## Coding Conventions
- Language: Vietnamese for UI text, English for code/comments
- Components: PascalCase, one per file
- API routes: REST, return { data } or { error }
- Always use Zod for API input validation
- Never expose S3 bucket name or raw URLs to client
- Presigned URLs: 15-minute TTL maximum
- All async Server Components, no useEffect for data fetching

## Security Rules
- Admin routes: always check HMAC cookie in middleware
- User uploads: not allowed — admin only
- File serving: always via /api/documents/[id]/proxy, never direct S3
- Video: signed URL with short TTL via /api/documents/[id]/stream
- Rate limit: unlock and share endpoints

## Dark Mode
- Always dark: bg-zinc-950, text-zinc-50
- Cards: bg-zinc-900 border-zinc-800
- Muted text: text-zinc-400
- Accent: violet-500 / violet-600
